                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen-rich coking process suitable for low-carbon metallurgy",
                    "一种适应低碳冶金的富产氢气的焦化工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a hydrogen-rich coking process suitable for low-carbon metallurgy, which comprises the following steps: 1) through coal blending and coking processes, high-temperature raw gas is obtained while coke is produced by a coke oven; and 2) cooling the coke through dry quenching, and recovering heat to produce high-temperature superheated steam. And (3) the high-temperature raw gas is not cooled, and is directly subjected to non-catalytic oxidation reforming under the action of oxygen to obtain the high-temperature hydrogen-rich reducing gas. And 4) cooling the high-temperature hydrogen-rich reducing gas through a waste heat boiler to obtain high-temperature superheated steam, and purifying the hydrogen-rich reducing gas to obtain chemical byproducts. And (5) after high-temperature superheated steam in the steps (2) and (4) is connected, waste heat power generation is conducted to obtain electric energy. The coke product produced by the invention meets the requirement of the hydrogen-rich blast furnace, and the byproduct high-temperature raw gas is used for preparing the low-carbon low-cost hydrogen-rich reducing gas, so that the whole coking process flow is optimized, and low-carbon hydrogen is obtained and the carbon emission in the whole coking production process is reduced while the coke is produced in an energy-saving and consumption-reducing manner."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种适应低碳冶金的富产氢气的焦化工艺，包括：1)通过配煤和炼焦工艺，焦炉生产焦炭的同时得到高温荒煤气。2)焦炭通过干熄焦降温后，回收热量生产高温过热蒸汽。3)高温荒煤气不降温，在氧气的作用下直接进行非催化氧化重整得到高温富氢还原气。4)高温富氢还原气通过余热锅炉降温后，得到高温过热蒸汽，富氢还原气进行净化处理，得到化工副产品。5)步骤2)和4)中高温过热蒸汽并网后进行余热发电获得电能。本发明生产的焦炭产品在满足富氢高炉需求的同时，副产品高温荒煤气用于制备低碳低成本富氢还原气，优化整个炼焦工艺流程，在节能降耗生产焦炭的同时，获得低碳氢气，降低整个焦化生产过程的碳排放。"
                }
            ]
